OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783793977
OL,3,CTeenager dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty at Dovestone Reservoir
OL,6,FGreater Manchester Police, Greater
OL,7,FManchester Fire and Rescue were taking
OL,8,Fpart in the extensive search operation
OL,9,Fnear Oldham.
OL,11,FA teenager has died following a major
OL,12,Fsearch and rescue operation at
OL,13,FDovestone Reservoir after reports a
OL,14,Fperson had got into difficulty in the
OL,15,Fwater.
OL,17,FThe 18-year-old was found unresponsive
OL,18,Fat around 8pm on Friday 10th July, and
OL,19,Fwas pronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
