PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783793977
OL,3,CTeenager dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty at Dovestone Reservoir
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Steven Horton
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have tragically recovered
OL,8,Fthe body of an 18-year-old man from
OL,9,Fthe water and are conducting extensive
OL,10,Fenquiries to establish the full
OL,11,Fcircumstances.
OL,13,F"Our thoughts remain with his family
OL,14,Fand friends during this incredibly
OL,15,Fdifficult time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783793977
OL,3,CTeenager dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty at Dovestone Reservoir
OL,6,F"I would like to take this opportunity
OL,7,Fto remind the public of the dangers of
OL,8,Fopen water. We strongly encourage
OL,9,Fpeople to stay safe and refrain from
OL,10,Fentering large bodies of water
OL,11,Fincluding reservoirs, rivers, canals,
OL,12,For ponds"
OL,14,F"Your safety is our priority. Please
OL,15,Flook after yourselves and enjoy the
OL,16,Fweather safely."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
