OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783793977
OL,3,CTeenager dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty at Dovestone Reservoir
OL,6,FWitnesses reported seeing a major
OL,7,Femergency services presence at the
OL,8,FSaddleworth beauty spot, with several
OL,9,Fpolice cars, fire engines, ambulances
OL,10,Fand an air ambulance called to the
OL,11,Fscene.
OL,13,FIt's the second tragedy in Greater
OL,14,FManchester in just 24 hours, following
OL,15,Fon from the death of a 49 year old man
OL,16,Fafter he got into difficulty at Sykes
OL,17,Freservoir at Alexandra Park in the
OL,18,FEdgeley area of Stockport on Thursday
OL,19,Fnight.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
