FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783793977
OL,3,CTeenager dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty at Dovestone Reservoir
OL,6,FIt brings to 11 the number of people
OL,7,Fin the North West who have died in
OL,8,Fwater-related incidents this year.
OL,10,FAn amber heat-health alert is in place
OL,11,Ffor most of England until 9pm on
OL,12,FSunday, 12 July, with some areas
OL,13,Fexpected to get temperatures of up to
OL,14,F33 degrees.
OL,16,FIssued by the UK Health Security
OL,17,FAgency (UKHSA) in partnership with the
OL,18,FMet Office, the warning was escalated
OL,19,Ffrom yellow to amber on Thursday, 9
OL,20,FJuly, as temperatures continue to
OL,21,Fclimb across the region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,362,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1783793977
OL,3,CTeenager dies after getting into
OL,4,Cdifficulty at Dovestone Reservoir
OL,6,FThe amber status indicates that the
OL,7,Fhigh temperatures could have
OL,8,Fsignificant impacts across the health
OL,9,Fand social care sector, posing
OL,10,Fincreased risks to vulnerable people
OL,11,Fand those with pre-existing health
OL,12,Fconditions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
